HEADWORD: Additament
<hw>Ad*dit"a*ment</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧d*d⟦icr⟧t"⟦adot⟧*m⟦eit⟧nt)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>additamentum</ets>, fr. <ets>additus</ets>,
